sociales acquises &#x00E0; compter de l&#x2019;ann&#x00E9;e de l&#x2019;ann&#x00E9;e d&#x2019;imposition&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; sanctionner la non-d&#x00E9;claration des biens dont le montant, sup&#x00E9;rieur &#x00E0; 50 000&#x20AC;, ne serait pas en ad&#x00E9;quation avec les revenus du contribuable, et ce dans le but de lutter contre les revenus issus d&#x2019;activit&#x00E9;s ill&#x00E9;gales. La sanction pr&#x00E9;vue pourra &#x00EA;tre maintenue tant que le contribuable n&#x2019;aura pas justifi&#x00E9; de cette disproportion selon les mentions de l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a 3.<br>Tel est le sens de cet amendement.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-19", "datePublication": "2024-10-23", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-10-23T23:40:44+02:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B0324P1D1N002929?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2025IDS28589", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "CGI", "divisionCodeLoi": "168"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XML